\frac{d}{dt}f(x(t),y(t),\ldots, z(t)) = \frac{\partial f}{\partial x}\frac{dx}{dt}+\frac{\partial y}{\partial t}+\cdots+\frac{\partial f}{\partial z}\frac{dz}{dt}.
